<p class="question" id="250552"><strong>Q. </strong>Which is the best supplement for muscle building ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>Protein, Creatine and Aminos combination is
                       best for muscle building. A multivitamin can also be taken with these supplements. Protein
                       requirement for muscle
                       building is atleast 2 -3 grams per kg body weight.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250700"><strong>Q. </strong>
  In how many days can we see results of muscle building ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>If the right supplements are taken regularly with an exercise
                       schedule, muscle building takes at least 2 -3 months time. A good protein diet helps in faster
                       and better results.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250856"><strong>Q. </strong>
  What if we stop taking these supplements?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>If you stop taking the supplements, you need to take provide the
                       right amount of protein from the diet. However 2 scoops of protein daily is recommended for
                       maintaining good muscle
                       mass.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250857"><strong>Q. </strong>
  How to increase Biceps size / Stamina ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>Creatine helps to increase stamina and muscle size by increasing the
                       oxygen supply to the muscles. Creatine should be taken with a protein supplement for best
                       results.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>


<p class="question" id="250858"><strong>Q. </strong>
  What to do for joints pain during exercises?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>You can take calcium -magnesium supplement and omega 3 supplements
                       for relieving joints pain.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250859"><strong>Q. </strong>
  Which is the best supplement for weight gain ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong> For weight gain, you need to take a weight
                        gainer supplement which has the right combination of proteins, carbohydrates and fat to provide
                        the extra calories
                        for gaining weight. A good multivitamin will help in increasing appetite and improving
                        metabolism, thus helping in
                        weight gain.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250860"><strong>Q. </strong>
  Which is the best supplement for muscle mass gain ? </p>

<p><strong>A. </strong> Supplement with a high protein content and
                        equivalent amount of carbohydrates will help in building lean muscle mass. A multivitamin with
                        amino supplement will
                        also be beneficial for lean mass gain.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250861"><strong>Q. </strong>
  Which is the best supplement for muscle mass gain ? </p>

<p><strong>A. </strong> You need to take a good rich-calorie diet to
                        increase your calorie intake. Eat healthy foods every 3 hours. You should have 5 -6 meals daily,
                        3 heavy meals
                        (breakfast, lunch, dinner) and 2 -3 in between meals.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250862"><strong>Q. </strong>
  In how many days can we see results ? </p>

<p><strong>A. </strong> Weight gain depends on individual metabolism.
                        However 4 - 5 kg weight gain per month can be expected with a good weight gainer and a balanced
                        diet. </p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

<p class="question" id="250863"><strong>Q. </strong>
  Is gym workouts a must for weight gain ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>Gym workouts are not a must for weight gain.
                       However light exercises at home or morning-evening walks are recommended when taking weight
                       gainer supplements for
                       uniform weight gain and proper digestion.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

