<p><strong>A. </strong>Fat burners mainly have herbs that help to
                       increase metabolic rate and accelerate the fat loss process. They do not have side-effects if
                       taken in the
                       recommended dose.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>

