<p class="question" id="250866"><strong>Q. </strong>
  How many days do we see fat loss results ?</p>

<p><strong>A. </strong>Fat loss depends on a number of factors like
                       individual metabolic rate, diet, lifestyle, exercises, genetic structure to name a few. However
                       on an average, with
                       proper exercises and diet plan, one can see 3 -4 kg weight loss in a month’s time.</p>

<div align="right" style="margin-right:10px;"><a href="#top">back to top &uarr;</a></div>


